Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the Great Pirate Era is coming to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the Straw Hats have left Fishman Island and are headed for the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:47.28,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Z's Ambition! Lily the Little Giant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, there, everywhere! 360 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Navy could accomplish this. They know every move that we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally surrounded. There is nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, stop talking in such a cool manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're closing in on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep moving forward like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They outnumber us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, get ready to fire at them! Chopper, fill the tank with cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the sides to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gigant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The warships are vanishing one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're seeing was a mirage only found in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop your guard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge raindrops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this weather?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the Maubeugemour Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momemomejuban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, "Maubeugemour"! Also known as the "Ill-Tempered Sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Home to weather conditions you've never seen or heard of before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hail? --It's such a dangerous sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna hit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,360-...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's an avalanche from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It started raining hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's just rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The water split!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty much anything goes here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is done, we're gonna end up back in the deep sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll hit a rock and drown before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing phenomenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to be impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--Cut. --Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to the Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--Cool! --He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's baking hot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's sweltering... --That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm impressed, Nami-san. You know about the weather in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I studied as much as I could about the New World over the past 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a beer when it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm hungry! --Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! We caught a deep-sea fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, most of it was ruined by the horrible weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had already set aside some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me some time and I'll cook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll just whip up some carpaccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's soup will be deep-sea fish bouillabaisse. What should I make for the main dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's done! Come and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Food! Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it and wait. It's deep-sea fish carpaccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's nothing here! --No, it's on the platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a platter here but nothing is on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Boo! Boo! --Did you guys eat it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Maubeugemour Sea is haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The soup is all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A bug ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did the bug eat it?! --No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The strawberries are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?! The corn is gone! --Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, it went outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--The fridge is empty! --What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?! I lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--What's going on? --We found a bug ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And a food thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "thief"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ate what I found sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we call a "thief"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why are you doing this to me, Luffy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where? --Oh? Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All the food in the fridge is gone too! The booze as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you steal my food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey, catch her, Franky! --I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get caught now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She took Franky down! She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we gotta go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the Mini-Mini Full Rebound!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, mega young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh no! --She's gonna stab us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, he lifted her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Propeller!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Propeller Wind-Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? She can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Young girl, I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, she's a Devil Fruit user.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she shrinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--She woke up. --Young girl, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Don't use violence against a lady again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can grow and shrink! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was born a Giant but I ate the Mini-Mini Fruit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but this is my usual size now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I can shrink myself down to 5 millimeters and enlarge myself to the size of the Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... You're interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Am I? --Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're strong too! Although you're small, you took Franky down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm small, I still have the power of the Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He totally forgot that she ate all of our food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have another technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get smaller and slip into my enemy's body
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then expand myself to break him into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, I can become a Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is a rubber man. So instead of breaking into pieces, he stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! You're right, how interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, young girl, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Lily Enstomach. People call me "Lily the Glutton"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I eat a lot for a woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily, why are you aboard this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when your ship flew out of the water all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were you waiting for in the middle of nowhere like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be wasting my time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lily-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! The size of your head doesn't match your body anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottle was shattered! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally made it this far by sneaking aboard some Navy boats and warships!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get to my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad? Are you looking for your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is the greatest pirate chef in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate chef? Lily-chan, what's your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Panz Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he that famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a top volcano cooking chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Volcano cooking?! What's that? Is it delicious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I'm getting excited just by thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my favorite food - churrasco sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rare herbs that only grow around volcanoes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and million-year-old salt crystals from between molten rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All sprinkled on sea monster meat and stewed in a volcano
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to cook it up quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all! The best one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A frying pan filled with an assortment of foods from the sea and mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...all cooked over a volcano! It's called Thousand-Person Paella!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one taste and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like slipping into a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like running through a field of flowers in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat it! I wanna run in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly food! Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about Panz Fry before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He steals food from the Government, the Navy, and other pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and likes nothing better than to cook for starving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero? I'm flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time to be flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with that. Tell us what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I was pirating around with Dad for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but he went missing all of a sudden a couple weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the Navy took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asking around going island to island
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then I read in the paper that he'll be taken to Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Impel Down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? He's a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Dad has a 320-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 300 million?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept stealing food from the Government and the Navy so the price went up before he knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I managed to get this far but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...the ship I was on was wrecked by this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good girl! You love your dad so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But of all places - Impel Down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That prison has no mercy. I almost died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was hiding in a warship, I heard them talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're traveling across the Maubeugemour Sea carrying Panz Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship carrying Dad will pass through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Navy is coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they see us, it's not gonna be pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But I have to save Dad at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they take him to Impel Down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my last chance to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause you guys trouble anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just give me an empty bottle, I'll get off of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys better get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna try that heavenly food that only your dad can make!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, he's a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we do. So don't worry, Lily-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't help her now, it's a dishonor to our pervert name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first fight in the New World will be against the Navy! I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be karma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When we rescue him, let me have some of that heavenly volcano food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you have enough until your stomach bursts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuzo-san! Come in! Shuzo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want? Our commander is unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships were required to turn out today. Why aren't you here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? Answer me! Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you, Shuzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to the Maubeugemour Sea soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you taking such a long way round?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You obviously don't understand how important this plan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Then why... --I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...that a ship carrying Panz Fry, that big-shot pirate, will pass through the Maubeugemour Sea soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna miss this opportunity and let him continue to live in Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All pirates in the New World must be exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was what we Neo Navy really want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give the Navy onto our plan by letting you do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You better come here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sink him with the Navy and all, there'll be no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pull off this operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...and prove that I will be a better right-hand man to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail... You know the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the foolish Navy realize how formidable we Neo Navy are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what's going on with the weather now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirage, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Visibility is going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be harder to find your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lily, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.06,OS,,0,0,0,,SIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and take Lily's dad back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami's plan to rescue Lily's father is put into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But events take an unexpected turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and escalate into a full-scale war between the Straw Hats and the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the fierce battle concludes and the rescue appears successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...both the Straw Hats and Navy are attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...by a new enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Z's Ambition! A Dark and Powerful Army!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
